Need to add a button to pause the proxy at any time on the dashboard, that way the site can still be up but the proxy is not functioning (this way the server actually never goes down and i dont have to painstakenly restart it and deal with the SSL cert)

Need manyyyy more stats, tracking how many of x api was requested, how many requests, how long, average time between requests and individual request types, and everything

Whenever an error happens I need to email it to myself if possible

Need a way to view, in real-time, the current stuff being requested, the ip, user agent, headers, body, url, all of it

Should send an email to myself whenever someone logs into the admin page, I should also provide a link to instantly invalidate the token in that email

- Save every endpoint people try to go to and see the most common ones and the frequency and last done
- Whenever I successfully log in, minus 1 from the admin page visits
- save everything to a file with minified JSON to keep track of stats without an RDS or something similar
- need to make the front-end scroll, especially on mobile (also it gets cut off on stuff like the )
- log the vulnerabilities that bots are checking and create a big log of it
- need to recode the proxy script to be better and more robust
- I should save the most frequent crawlers and endpoints spammers instead if removing them once it hits 20
- add separate metric for retries (and what the status code was for each and the reason)
- more robust reason returning and logging. Also need to denote if a reason returned was custom or roblox's
- if the visitor of a page is a potential crawler (user agent check?) then count them in a different visitor count so I can better tell the actual visitor count
- increase the 2fa time like damn (60 seconds)

